snippet.title: Cook For Love | Teaser Trailer | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Win the hearts of Parisians with your cooking, discover delicious recipes, and
become a chef worthy of working onboard the Orient Express!

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3009920/Cook_For_Love/?beta=0

Don't forget to follow us on 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RedDeer_Games
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/RedDeerGames
and Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/reddeer_games/
